    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "We need now to give special attention to the cultivation of character. Let this mind be in you that was in Christ Jesus, that it may elevate and ennoble the highest as also the lowest worker in our Sabbath schools, so that Jesus will not be ashamed to acknowledge them as His colaborers. All spiritual culture Christ has provided for His children. If Jesus is abiding in the soul, the heart is filled with the holy graces of His Spirit, which makes itself manifest in the transforming of the features. If you would have beauty and loveliness of character, the divine law must be written upon the heart and carried out in the life.&mdash;<span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"TSS 20.1\" data-link=\"121.70\"><em>Testimonies on Sabbath-School Work</em>, 20-22</span>.",
